### Smart Task - ProjectController API Test
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Auth
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Dynamic IDs
@workspaceId = REPLACE_WORKSPACE_ID
@projectId = REPLACE_PROJECT_ID

### 1) Create project (workspace owner/admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Project Alpha",
  "description": "Mobile app MVP"
}

### 2) Get all projects by workspace (workspace member can view)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3) Update project (workspace owner/admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Project Alpha Updated",
  "description": "Updated scope"
}

### 4) Delete project (workspace owner/admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
